INNER JOIN [PROYECTO] AS [p] ON [i].[IDPROYECTO] = [p].[ID]
WHERE [i].[FECHA_PAGO] IS NOT NULL AND (DATEPART(year, [i].[FECHA_PAGO]) = @__anio_0)
GROUP BY DATEPART(month, [i].[FECHA_PAGO]), [i].[IDPROYECTO], [p].[NOMBRE]

    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[ID]
    ELSE 0
END AS [IdSegmento], CASE
    WHEN [s].[ID] IS NOT NULL THEN [s].[NOMBRE]
    ELSE ''
END AS [NombreSegmento], [c].[CUENTA] AS [Cuenta], [c].[IDCUENTA] AS [IdCuenta], [g].[MONTO] AS [Monto], [g].[FECHA] AS [Fecha], [g].[OBSERVACION] AS [Observacion], [g].[ESTADO] AS [Estado], [g].[VENTA] AS [Venta]
FROM [PROYECTO] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [GASTOSEJECUCION] AS [g] ON [p].[ID] = [g].[IDPROYECTO]
INNER JOIN [GASTOS] AS [g0] ON [g].[IDGASTO] = [g0].[ID]
LEFT JOIN [SEGMENTO] AS [s] ON [g].[SEGMENTO] = [s].[ID]
INNER JOIN [CUENTA] AS [c] ON [g0].[IDCUENTA] = [c].[ID]
WHERE [p].[ID] = @__idproyecto_0

    WHEN ([g].[ESTADO] <> 'Forecast') OR [g].[ESTADO] IS NULL THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [g].[FECHA]

FROM [INGRESOSREALES] AS [i]

SELECT DATEPART(month, [i].[FECHA_PAGO]) AS [Mes], [p].[NOMBRE] AS [Proyecto], COALESCE(SUM([i].[MONTOCLP]), 0.0) AS [Total]

INNER JOIN [PROYECTO] AS [p] ON [i].[IDPROYECTO] = [p].[ID]
WHERE ([i].[FECHA_PAGO] IS NOT NULL AND (DATEPART(year, [i].[FECHA_PAGO]) = @__anio_0)) AND ([i].[ESTADO] = 'Pagada')
GROUP BY DATEPART(month, [i].[FECHA_PAGO]), [i].[IDPROYECTO], [p].[NOMBRE]

INNER JOIN [STATUS_PROYECTO] AS [s] ON [p].[STATUS_PROYECTO] = [s].[ID]
WHERE DATEPART(year, [p].[FECHA_INICIO]) = @__anio_0
GROUP BY [s].[TIPO_STATUS]
